This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the optimization of inference procedures in deep neural networks. Additionally, the paper also involves computer vision (cs.CV) as it mentions state-of-the-art networks such as AlexNet, VGG-16, ResNet152, and DenseNet. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with the optimization of neural networks. The paper also involves neural networks (cs.NE) as it deals with the optimization of dot product operations in deep neural networks. Finally, the paper also involves data structures (cs.DS) as it presents new efficient representations for matrices with low entropy statistics.
